title: Gov. Ricketts determined to address problems in Whiteclay
text: LINCOLN, Neb. (AP) - Nebraska Gov. Pete Ricketts says he's determined to address the problems that plague the village of Whiteclay and is working with a Native American activist to seek solutions.
